ļGood night sweet Prince and may
flights of angels sing you to your rest.
Thank you for being my friend.
JD

Neil Young
11th April 1961 - 15th July 2019
You were our sunshine
Ali, Izzie, Charlotte, Family & Friends
Forever in our hearts"¾
­Tim Slane walked these Battersea paths all his life
drawing solace & inspiration from this oasis.
Rest here and see what he saw, look up & see the canopy
& the life in it, making its way as he did
Sadly missed. Tim Slane, 58 years young"¾
